Title: Lyckliga skitar
Writer: Bernt Lundquist, Vilgot Sjöman, Solveig Ternström
Actors: Bernt Lundquist, Solveig Ternström, Tomas Bolme, Inger Liljefors
Plot: A bachelor truck driver meet a pregnant woman. She moves in with him. Days turn into weeks and the bachelor considers becoming the stepfather to the child.
